        <bioghist id="ref9">
            <head>Biographical Note</head>
            <p>Captain, United States Army Transportation Corps; member, 762nd Railway Shop Battalion, 1942-1946.</p>
        </bioghist>
        <scopecontent id="ref10">
            <head>Scope and Content of Collection</head>
            <p>Personnel records, orders, letters, manuals, servicemen's newspapers, clippings, other printed matter, photographs, and miscellany relating to American military railway service operations in Iran and elsewhere in the Persian Gulf Command during World War II.</p>
        </scopecontent>
