                <scopecontent id="ref39">
                    <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
                    <p>Includes memoranda, orders, invitations, passes, certificates, receipts, and ephemera relating to Hill's service in Iran and time spent in Palestine, Germany, and Paris on leave or in connection with his Army service. Also includes a small amount of material related to Claude Hovis, Hill's roommate, who was killed in Iran.</p>
                </scopecontent>
            </c01>
